dininginfo.name: The Bistro
dininginfo.description:
The Bistro
is a modern eatery featuring an open kitchen, sushi bar, and an exciting Pacific Rim-inspired menu. Our chefs draw from various Asian cultures to serve up the freshest seafood,crisp greens, local produce inspired vegetarian fare, and noodle dishes. The ideal experience focuses on tasting a variety of flavors and sharing plates with friends.
Online reservations are strongly encouraged. For parties greater than 10,
please call 858.822.4275
dininginfo.location: The Strand at The Village East
